                     <origDate notBefore="1850" notAfter="1900">The scribe <persName ref="PRS10788WaldaMuse" role="scribe">Walda Muse</persName> 
                        was active in the second half of the 19th century; he was a contemporary of <persName ref="PRS10378Yohanne"/> (r. 1872-89) and Metropolitan ʾAtnātewos (in tenure 1869-76) (cp. <ref type="mss" corresp="ESagm009"/>, <ref type="mss" corresp="ESmr004"/>,  <ref type="mss" corresp="ESmr006"/>, <ref type="mss" corresp="ESmr007"/>,
